WEBVTT

00:00.607 --> 00:05.770
Here are some phrases you can use when starting and ending a conversation.

00:07.433 --> 00:08.897
Long time no see.

00:10.809 --> 00:12.488
Is this your first time here?

00:14.329 --> 00:15.627
Do you come here often?

00:17.446 --> 00:20.263
Hello! I wanted to introduce myself.

00:21.984 --> 00:23.769
Hi! Do you have a minute?

00:25.626 --> 00:27.715
I don't want to keep you any longer.

00:29.536 --> 00:30.895
I'll let you carry on then.

00:32.795 --> 00:34.650
Thanks again for the great time!

00:36.466 --> 00:38.028
I have got to get going.

00:39.774 --> 00:41.415
I shall now head out.

